channel.title: QuarterX Server Team
channel.description:
[center][size=40pt]QuarterX Server Team[/size]
[b]What is QuarterX Server Team?[/b] [i]QuarterX Server Team is simply a team of highly skilled coders to produce one of the best 317 out there yet. The jobs will consist of Server Coder, Client Coder, Cache Editor (Maybe), Forum Leader, Web Client Maker, and don't forget the Testers, who help find bugs.
[b]What are we planning on making?[/b] [i]QuarterX Server Team is planning on making one of the best 317 servers out there. The source we are making will most likely be for release, unless we can get a good hoster. It will be open source to anybody who would be deemed to want it.
[b]How do I sign up?[/b] [i]To sign up, simply fill out a form and we will contact you A.S.A.P with our answer. Here is the application you are going to need to fill out to join:
[code] QuarterX Server Team Application -------------------------------------- 1. Name: 2. Age: 3. What job would you like: 4. What is your past experience: 5. MSN: 6. Any extra info: [/code]
Please simply fill that out and post it. We will contact you A.S.A.P.
On the list below, even though all the -'s are filled, doesn't mean you can't become one.
[size=30pt]Server Team[/size]
[b]Leader[/b] -Mrquarter
[b]Server Coders[/b] - Muhascape Owner - Sane - MighteZezima
[b]Client Coders[/b] - MighteZezima - Doggiedoo86 -
[b]Cache Editor[/b] - Harleyscape Owner - Doggiedoo86 -
[b]Forum Maker[/b] - Planplan - P0unding - Goddess
[b]Web Client Developers[/b] - - -
Thanks, QuarterX Server Team[/center]
